author: KEXP
title: Our latest Live on KEXP session from Mexico features Peruvian songwriter La Zorra Zapata. Watch now.

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG and Vive Latino present Live on KEXP from Mexico City with La Zorra Zapata performing at El Desierto Casa Estudio. Recorded October 16, 2024.

Songs:
Increíble 00:38
El Invento 05:47
Oficio 10:05
Acantilados 14:39

Nuria Zapata – Vocals and guitar
Ruiz González – Backing vocals, guitar, and SPD

Live on KEXP in Mexico City is a partnership with Vive Latino celebrating its 25th anniversary with the support of Indie Rocks! Magazine. Recorded at El Desierto Casa Estudio in Desierto de Los Leones, Mexico.

Host: Albina Cabrera
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
Editor: Luke Knecht

Recorded By Matt Ogaz & JC Vertti
Assistant Engineer: Sebastián Garrido
Mastered by Matt Ogaz

Studio Manager: Gabriela Sandoval
Artist Coordinator (Vive Latino): Irma Celio
Audio Production Manager (Vive Latino): Paola Silva

Vive Latino Support:
Jordi Puig
Itzel Flores

https://lazorrazapata.bandcamp.com
